
The app gets the current location's coordinates and uses them to retrieve the weather data from OpenWeatherMap.org.
It displays the current temperature and weather conditions as well as a today's forecast and a 5 day forecast.
It can save favourite locations (however loading is not yet implemented) .
It implements a refresh data feature.
The implementation of a side bar menu that would display the favourite locations is yet to be defined.
Working time 3h 11mins
